overview: Maruthi, a son of a shopkeeper falls in love with Deepika, the only sister of Prathap Reddy, a zamindar and has deep political connections and believes in the caste system. Things take a fatal turn when Deepika accepts Maruthi`s love. Will Maruthi and Deepika be able to fight all odds and live happily ever after?
title: Nenu C/o Nuvvu
